        <p>Water inlet valve failure — the valve had failed closed, stopping all water flow into the machine. The machine was cycling normally through its refrigeration sequence but without water entering, no ice could form. The valve screen also had significant scale buildup from the Pasadena water supply (similar hardness to LA proper), which had contributed to the valve failure over time.</p>
